<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idbf3d9c6e-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s11272"><num value="11272">§ 11272.</num><heading> Dissemination</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Administrator of the Centers for Medicare &amp; Medicaid Services shall disseminate the results of research conducted under this part to appropriate professional entities and to the public.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idbf3d9c6f-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">(<ref href="/us/pl/99/660/tIX/s938">Pub. L. 99–660, title IX, § 938</ref>, formerly § 949B, <date date="1986-11-14">Nov. 14, 1986</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/100/3812">100 Stat. 3812</ref>; renumbered § 938, <ref href="/us/pl/100/607/tI/s142/c/2/B">Pub. L. 100–607, title I, § 142(c)(2)(B)</ref>, <date date="1988-11-04">Nov. 4, 1988</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/102/3057">102 Stat. 3057</ref>; amended <ref href="/us/pl/108/173/tIX/s900/e/5/C">Pub. L. 108–173, title IX, § 900(e)(5)(C)</ref>, <date date="2003-12-08">Dec. 8, 2003</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/117/2373">117 Stat. 2373</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
